  "Description": {
    "English": "A set of complex hydraulic tubes and various gripping surfaces that form a pair of usable arms for a <span class=\"name name-technology\">primitive automaton</span>.<br><br>Plans for this unit were extracted from an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">autophage</span> left at an abandoned junker's camp.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "复杂的液压管道与各种抓握面构成了为<span class=\"name name-technology\">基础自动装置</span>准备的一对实用手臂。<br><br>该单元的制作图提取自废弃拾荒者营地中的一个<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自噬体</span>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "成套的複雜液壓管路及各式抓握表面，形成一對可用的<span class=\"name name-technology\">原始機械生物</span>手臂。<br><br>此單位的設計圖來自被棄置在廢棄拾荒者營地的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">自噬</span>。"
  },
